Class SDuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.datatype.Duration
      • cz.syntea.xdef.sys.SDuration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<SDuration>

    public class SDuration
extends javax.xml.datatype.Duration
implements java.lang.Comparable<SDuration>
    Provides operations with date and time periods (see ISO 8061). This class implements abstract methods from javax.xml.datatype.Duration.
